-/**
- * bitmap_parselist - convert list format ASCII string to bitmap
- * @buf: read user string from this buffer; must be terminated
- *    with a \0 or \n.
- * @maskp: write resulting mask here
- * @nmaskbits: number of bits in mask to be written
